snippet.title: CookieSwirlC
snippet.description:
⋆◕‿◕⋆ 

Hi I’m Cookie. Welcome to my variety channel that I started in 2013 (OMG soo long ago!)  I LOVE fun so I created this channel to share my passions with my awesome fans. I think little collectibles and dolls are so cute. I love to create stories and play out different voices by acting out each character. I stand for Love, Kindness, Fun, and Creativity 🎨 

I believe you can do anything and that being kind to yourself and others is the start to happiness.  I hope my videos bring you a smile 🤗😊


🍪 Roblox Group  Forever Cookie Fans:  www.roblox.com/groups/12537219/Forever-Cookie-Fans#!/store
🍪 INSTAGRAM: @cookiewirlc
🍪 TWITER: @cookieswirlc
🍪 MERCH SHOP:  https://teespring.com/stores/cookieswirlc
🍪 ROBLOX SHOP:  https://www.roblox.com/catalog/?Category=3&Subcategory=3&CreatorName=PlayCookiePlay

❤ Amazing Banner Artwork by @peikomei on Instagram




CookieSwirlC does NOT have Facebook, Snapchat or TikTok
